thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by KIM

author: KIM
title: KIM
text: The product, a self-inking stamp, was exactly as ordered. The quality of the stamp and the ink impression are excellent. The lettering and outline of the impression are sharp and distinct. I was impressed with the very reasonable cost of the item; and, super-fast delivery. I was "wowed"!
